# Cline Rules for PyCon JP 2025 Chair's Blog

## File Structure
- All blog posts should be placed in the `_posts` directory
- Follow Jekyll's naming convention: `YYYY-MM-DD-title.md` for all posts
- Use `-ja` suffix for Japanese posts and `-en` suffix for English posts when creating paired content

## Frontmatter
- Japanese posts should include:
  ```yaml
  ---
  title: [Japanese title]
  layout: default
  permalink: /[slug]-ja.html
  ---
  ```

- English posts should include:
  ```yaml
  ---
  lang: en
  title: [English title]
  layout: default
  permalink: /[slug]-en.html  # Optional
  ---
  ```

## Content Guidelines
- Start Japanese posts with: "PyCon JP 2025 座長 [@nishimotz](https://d.nishimotz.com/aboutme) が個人として公開する日報です。"
- Include event information: "[PyCon JP 2025](https://2025.pycon.jp/) は9月26日・27日に広島国際会議場で開催されます。"
- Include recruitment information when appropriate: "主催メンバーを募集しています。[主催メンバー申し込みフォーム](https://forms.gle/7irqYKhZVj7AY7LfA)からご応募ください。"
- Use `<div class="image-center">` for centered images
- End posts with an update history section:
  ```markdown
  ## 更新履歴
  - YYYY-MM-DD: 初版公開
  ```

## Markdown Formatting
- Use ATX-style headers (`#` for h1, `##` for h2, etc.)
- Use link references in the format `[text](url)`
- Use image references in the format `![alt text]({{ site.baseurl }}/assets/images/image.webp)`
- Place all images in the `assets/images/` directory

## Theme and Concept
- PyCon JP 2025のスローガンは "pieces of python, coming together" です（まだ公開前）
- このコンセプトを念頭に置いて、コンテンツを作成してください
- "Python Circle" というコンセプトは不採用となったため、使用しないでください
- 広島開催の特別な意義やPython 3.14（π）との関連性については適宜触れてください

## Translation Guidelines
- When creating content in both languages, ensure the core information is consistent
- Adapt content for cultural context rather than providing literal translations
- Create separate files for each language version
- Link between language versions when appropriate

## Development Guidelines
- Test changes locally using `bundle exec jekyll serve --host 0.0.0.0 --incremental`
- Verify both Japanese and English content displays correctly

